On July 29, 2004, Atlantic Tele-Network, Inc. (the "Company") issued a press release announcing earnings results for the three and six months ended June 30, 2004. The full text of the press release issued in connection with the announcement is attached as Exhibit 99.1 to this Current Report on Form 8-K.
 
