Item 2.02 Results of Operations and Financial Condition
 
On April 29, 2005, Atlantic Tele-Network, Inc. (the "Company") issued a press release announcing earnings results for the three months ended March 31, 2005. The full text of the press release issued in connection with the announcement is attached as Exhibit 99.1 to this Current Report on Form 8-K.
 
 
The information in the report, including the exhibit hereto, shall not be deemed "filed" for purposes of Section 18 of the Securities Exchange Act of 1934 (the "Exchange Act") or otherwise subject to liabilities of that section, nor shall it be deemed incorporated by reference in any filing under the Securities Act of 1933 of the Exchange Act, except as expressly set forth by specific reference in such a filing.
 
