Item 2.02   Results of Operations and Financial Condition.
 
On February 28, 2008, Atlantic Tele-Network, Inc. (the "Company") issued a press release announcing financial results for the quarter and year ended December 31, 2007.  A copy of the press release is furnished herewith as Exhibit 99.1.
 
