Item 2.02               Results of Operations and Financial Condition.
 
On July 31, 2008, Atlantic Tele-Network, Inc. (the "Company") issued a press release announcing financial results for the three and six months ended June 30, 2008.  A copy of the press release is furnished herewith as Exhibit 99.1.
 
