(F)           Any defense based upon the failure of any drawing under any Letter of Credit to conform to the terms of such Letter of Credit ( any draft, certificate or other document presented pursuant to such Letter of Credit appears on its face to comply with the terms thereof), any nonapplication or misapplication by the beneficiary or any transferee of the proceeds of such drawing or any other act or omission of such beneficiary or transferee in connection with such Letter of Credit;
